{
  "title": "Show-off Earthy Dense Lentil Stir-fry",
  "description": "This gluten-free Syrian dish features a dense and earthy flavor profile with the addition of sazon seasoning for extra depth. Slow-cooked lentils make it an excellent show-off dinner option.",
  "cuisine": "Syrian",
